ivardefs.name: author

ivardefs.name: authoringTime
ivardefs.desc: Date and time when the selection of the referenced instances were made. It is (typically) different from the creation date of the selection resource, and from dates associated with the referenced instances (e.g. capture time of the referenced image).

ivardefs.name: description
ivardefs.desc:
Free text narrative description of the ImagingManifest.

ivardefs.name: identifier
ivardefs.desc: Unique identifier of the DICOM Key Object Selection (KOS) that this resource represents.

ivardefs.name: patient
ivardefs.desc: A patient resource reference which is the patient subject of all DICOM SOP Instances in this ImagingManifest.

ivardefs.name: study_
ivardefs.desc: Study identity and locating information of the DICOM SOP instances in the selection.
